# Context7 usage

When working with external libraries, frameworks, SDKs, APIs, or configuration examples, always use Context7 before proposing code.

Use Context7 especially for:
- NestJS
- Prisma
- Supabase
- React Native
- React Navigation
- TanStack React libraries
- ML Kit
- JWT / JWS
- QR code libraries
- SQLite offline storage
- Render deployment
- Oracle Cloud / Docker / CompreFace setup

Do not rely only on model memory for library-specific code.